{"tid":2492711,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《人民日報》: 香港恢復穩定但國安風險未消失 要防「黑暴」死灰復燃","createTime":"2021-04-17T10:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T10:36:23.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ad59de48e1d86cb20e95b3c6e44d71f4f020a376","tid":2492711,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:27:47.000Z","msg":"繼《國安法》和「完善」選舉制度的「組合拳」後，官媒《人民日報》評論文章指，「香港社會恢復穩定並不代表國家安全風險消失」，所以但凡危害國安的，「硬對抗」要「依法打擊」、「軟對抗」要「依法規管」，「防止黑暴死灰復燃」。<br />\n<br />\n連日來特首林鄭月娥和警務處處長鄧炳強，已多番發表針對傳媒的言論。而今日題為「香港人心思安，別有用心的鼓譟注定待勞」的《人民日報》評論文章就指，「香港由亂及治、由治到興，不會一蹴而就」，「面對『港獨』勢力蠢蠢欲動、外部勢力頻頻插手，香港維護國家安全的防波堤仍要不斷加固。」<br />\n<br />\n文章強調「凡危害國家安全的，屬『硬對抗』就依法打擊，屬『軟對抗』就依法規管，這是香港防止黑暴死灰復燃、掃除繁榮發展障礙的必要之舉。」<br />\n<br />\n文章雖無針對甚麼範疇，但提到日前「全民國家安全教育日」上，「香港內外一些勢力再次打著『民主』『人權』的旗號說三道四，對香港國安立法及完善選舉制度肆意指責」， 批評這是「借國家安全教育日的時機，為注定要接受法律制裁的反中亂港分子搖旗吶喊，同時妄圖挑起矛盾、蠱惑人心。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210417/5S7QLYJZKFDX5BCUCQZH6NWRTU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210417%2F5S7QLYJZKFDX5BCUCQZH6NWRTU%2F&d=8tl7d8txXkgslZB5fT8CL5Mi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=e570dd85\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210417%2F5S7QLYJZKFDX5BCUCQZH6NWRTU%2F&h=b9fd145a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210417/5S7QLYJZKFDX5BCUCQZH6NWRTU/</a>"},{"pid":"8dbe2e7018d595d53c6993a59933e8fd4023e8a5","tid":2492711,"uid":86509,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:28:18.000Z","msg":"黑警暴力日日發生<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc053c0d4265811c7c3e4045eed6ef7dcd92fef7","tid":2492711,"uid":177168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:28:52.000Z","msg":"軍事對抗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a7dffb50aedfc30f1fa8bbf994022b7dd0f6b4","tid":2492711,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:30:54.000Z","msg":"哦，<br />\n<br />\n借個位，<br />\n［香港民族存亡終局之戰］要戰勝共匪，救香港、救自己、救手足、救後代、滅藍絲，路只剩返一條<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2492364\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2492364</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"90c3030d74d68157a16dda99d1e673a7278ecdbe","tid":2492711,"uid":33984,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:31:43.000Z","msg":"紅暴由97 年開始已經入侵香港"},{"pid":"1e6ca040a37f527f6ca3eb6fa6dd6d212597382c","tid":2492711,"uid":3457,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:31:46.000Z","msg":"咩呀 唔係李亨利咩"},{"pid":"3cb7d699f761e5a678ed7b51005a14a291384bfd","tid":2492711,"uid":383344,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:36:09.000Z","msg":"提出教育日條友居心叵測<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n製造大台比人批鬥 仲比班狗上演忠誠廢物戲碼，廣東話天灭中共步操、831幼兒版，學童玩槍上FT 頭版。"},{"pid":"e04699f79cca118d53901ad0942fd8ee4b7689ec","tid":2492711,"uid":221490,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:36:23.000Z","msg":"永遠的稻草人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}